License Carve-Out for Third-Party-Derived Files

A subset of the Apex source files under `force-app/main/default/classes/` are
derivative works of third-party open-source projects and remain licensed
under their upstream licenses. The Business Source License 1.1 above does
not apply to these files. Full upstream attribution (project URLs, copyright
holders, original license texts) lives in `NOTICES.md`. The canonical text
of each upstream license is shipped at `LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt`,
`LICENSES/MIT.txt`, and `LICENSES/BSD-3-Clause.txt`.

